file.name: oauth2.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: info
  description: info
  version: 0.1.0

paths:
  /example/api:
    get:
      summary: summary
      description: description
      responses:
        200:
          description: response

components:
  securitySchemes:
    OAuth_2.0_Client_Credentials:
      type: oauth2
      description: OAuth 2.0 - Client Credentials
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          tokenUrl: "https://example.com/token"
          scopes:
            scope: scope description
